  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Randomized, single-blind trial in which one group of patients will be operated with a
      &quot;Mid-Vastus approach&quot; of the knee joint and the other group will undergo knee surgery with a
      &quot;Sub-Vastus approach&quot;.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
